æspa

Title: “Shining Like the Stars”
Artist: Aespa

[Intro: Karina & Winter]
(Shining, shining, shining)
We’re rising, we’re glowing—like the stars.
(Shining, shining, shining)
Can’t stop us now, we’re ready to go far.

[Verse 1: Ningning & Giselle]
In the darkness, we’re the spark that ignites,
Bringing the light, no fear, no disguise.

Power in our hearts, we’re unstoppable, you’ll see.

[Pre-Chorus: Karina & Winter]
We’re dancing in the night, no looking back,

No limits, no chains, we’re rising so high,

[Chorus: Aespa (Full Group)]
Shining like the stars, lighting up the sky,
No one can stop us, we’re ready to rise!
Futures are waiting, we’re taking control,
We’re shining like the stars, heart and soul!

Shining like the stars, you’ll see us glow,
No matter where we go, we’re always in control.
Lighting the way, we’re fearless and free,
Shining like the stars, we’re meant to be!

[Verse 2: Ningning & Giselle]
Out of the shadows, into the spotlight,
Every moment’s ours, we’re taking flight.
No holding back, we’re breaking the norm,
Like a comet we crash, we’re reborn.

Digital avatars in the virtual zone,
But our power’s real, we’re fully grown.
Together we stand, we rise as one,
Ruling the universe, we’re second to none.

[Pre-Chorus: Karina & Winter]
We’re dancing in the night, no looking back,
We’re chasing the stars, we’re on the attack.
No limits, no chains, we’re rising so high,
Shining like the stars, we’re ready to fly.

[Chorus: Aespa (Full Group)]
Shining like the stars, lighting up the sky,
No one can stop us, we’re ready to rise!
Futures are waiting, we’re taking control,
We’re shining like the stars, heart and soul!

Shining like the stars, you’ll see us glow,
No matter where we go, we’re always in control.
Lighting the way, we’re fearless and free,
Shining like the stars, we’re meant to be!

[Bridge: Karina & Winter (with electronic effects)]
(Shining, shining, shining, shining)
Feel the fire burning inside,
(Shining, shining, shining, shining)
We’re unstoppable, we’re reaching new heights.
(Shining, shining, shining, shining)
We’re the future, we’re breaking the mold,
(Shining, shining, shining, shining)
Watch us shine, watch us glow.

[Chorus: Aespa (Full Group)]
Shining like the stars, lighting up the sky,
No one can stop us, we’re ready to rise!
Futures are waiting, we’re taking control,
We’re shining like the stars, heart and soul!

Shining like the stars, you’ll see us glow,
No matter where we go, we’re always in control.
Lighting the way, we’re fearless and free,
Shining like the stars, we’re meant to be!

[Outro: Aespa (Karina & Winter)]
Shining like the stars, we’re infinite.
Lighting up the world, we’ll never quit.
(Shining, shining, shining)
We’re shining like the stars…
(Shining, shining, shining)
Forever and ever…

[End]

This song combines Aespa’s signature electronic-pop sound with powerful, anthem-like choruses. The lyrics focus on self-empowerment, breaking through limitations, and the group’s connection to their futuristic, digital identities, all while highlighting their ability to “shine like the stars” both in the virtual and real worlds. The bridge adds an extra level of intensity, building up for an epic final chorus.
